The bundled seeddb.bin is a community-maintained encryption-seed database
maintained by ihavamac and contributors. The original Windows tool that
inspired this port is "Batch CIA 3DS Decryptor" by matiffeder, with the
"Redux" rewrite by xxmichibxx.

The closed-source decrypt.exe shipped with the original Redux distribution
has been replaced in this port by an open-source NCCH-flags patcher
(native/patch/ncch_flags.c, MIT License).
